Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:29.70,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(800,800)\blur8}第一次  我知晓  你笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:34.38,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(800,0)\blur8}第一次  突然偶然相遇的爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:37.25,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur8}你温柔的声音也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:39.67,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur8}你爱哭的习惯也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:41.72,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur8}每多了解你一点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:45.51,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(0,800)\blur8}都是新的第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.89,0:22:49.27,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(800,0)\blur8}「第一次」牵手的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:52.10,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(0,800)\blur8}手指犹豫不决
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:55.73,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\blur8\an9}要是被讨厌了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.73,0:22:57.15,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\an9}想碰触又不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:22:59.69,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\an9}手指徘徊不定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:02.90,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)\blur8\an9}第一次  第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:08.79,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(800,0)\blur8}将不计其数的与你的「第一次」收集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:12.79,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur8}就像 0 变成 1 一般不断增加
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.79,0:23:18.75,EDCN - ep12,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(0,800)\blur8}两人一起  无论多少「第一次」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:21.21,EDCN - ep12,,0,200,0,,{\fad(800,0)\blur8\an9}都一起去寻找  交给你
